1
00:00:41,300 --> 00:00:43,580
=Kesempurnaan Kecilku=
(Diadaptasi dari novel "Kesulitan Persiapan Hamil")

2
00:00:50,700 --> 00:00:53,260
=Episode 12=

3
00:00:53,400 --> 00:00:53,960
Siapa?

4
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:56,000
Chun... Chun'er.

5
00:00:58,120 --> 00:00:58,800
Di mana anak ini?

6
00:00:59,480 --> 00:00:59,960
Chun'er.

7
00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:04,960
Kenapa anak ini
mengunci dirinya di luar?

8
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:23,840
Bibi.

9
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:25,320
Chun'er.

10
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:26,840
Apakah itu kau, Chun'er?

11
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:29,960
Bibi.

12
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:30,800
Chun'er, ada apa?

13
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:35,760
Saat aku pergi mengambil air,
sepertinya ada orang yang mengejarku.

14
00:01:35,760 --> 00:01:36,760
Aku sangat takut.

15
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:37,560
Jangan takut.

16
00:01:40,960 --> 00:01:41,920
Ada Bibi di sini.

17
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:46,280
Bibi, apa yang harus kita lakukan?

18
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:55,440
Apakah ada wajah baru yang datang
akhir-akhir ini?

19
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:58,320
Menantuku datang.
Dia akan tinggal beberapa hari.

20
00:01:59,080 --> 00:02:00,640
Benar.

21
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:02,760
Terdapat bintang tunggal di tubuhnya.

22
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,560
Dalam hidupnya,

23
00:02:04,880 --> 00:02:06,840
bisa mengendalikan langit
dan diri sendiri.

24
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:10,800
Suruh dia pulang ke tempat asalnya.

25
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:12,720
Pulang?

26
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:14,000
Tidak bisa.

27
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:16,000
Bagaimana denganku
jika dia pergi?

28
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:17,920
Jika kau terus ragu,

29
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:19,920
salah satu di antara kalian

30
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:23,560
pasti akan mengalami bencana mengerikan.

31
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:27,200
Ini.

32
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,200
Ambil ini.

33
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:32,000
Letakkan ini di bawah bantalmu.

34
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,080
Ia akan melindungi kalian
di saat genting.

35
00:02:34,480 --> 00:02:36,160
Hidup tanpa kekhawatiran.

36
00:02:37,480 --> 00:02:39,960
Terima kasih, Dewi.

37
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,160
Terima kasih banyak.

38
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,080
Berkat Anda,

39
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:49,800
beberapa kilogram ceri kami
bisa terjual habis.

40
00:02:51,320 --> 00:02:52,360
Sama-sama.

41
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:54,880
Aku pasti harus membantu masyarakat.

42
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:56,960
Kalian tenang saja.

43
00:02:56,960 --> 00:03:00,680
Pembeli yang aku cari
pasti memberikan harga paling tinggi.

44
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:01,680
Benar.

45
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:03,680
Anda lanjutkan saja,
kami pergi dulu.

46
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,400
- Baik.
- Terima kasih.

47
00:03:05,600 --> 00:03:06,600
Baik, sampai jumpa.

48
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:22,040
Halo, Shanshan.

49
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:25,800
Seingatku, kau punya teman
konsumen besar buah-buahan.

50
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:27,240
Tolong bantu aku cari tahu,

51
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:29,200
bagaimana perkembangan pasar ceri
tahun ini?

52
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:40,080
Ibu.

53
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:44,920
Kalian terburu-buru pergi ke mana
di pagi hari?

54
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:46,800
Nanti kuberi tahu.

55
00:03:56,880 --> 00:03:57,880
Aneh sekali.

56
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:20,040
Bibi, cepat lihat.

57
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:32,080
Bibi.

58
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:34,800
Tahi lalat bintang tunggal itu
benar-benar ada.

59
00:04:35,080 --> 00:04:36,920
Selanjutnya adalah bencana mengerikan.

60
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:39,800
Dewi bilang, Bibi tidak cocok dengannya.

61
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:42,360
Berikutnya,
pasti Bibi yang tidak beruntung.

62
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:43,680
Bagaimana ini?

63
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:46,240
Bukankah Dewi sudah memberi Bibi
banyak barang?

64
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:47,120
Biar aku ambilkan.

65
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:48,000
Benar juga.

66
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:52,440
Cepat, berikan padaku.

67
00:04:54,280 --> 00:04:55,520
Tolong berkati hamba.

68
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:56,200
Masih ada.

69
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:57,640
Tolong berkati hamba.

70
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,760
Masih ada, ini yang paling penting.

71
00:05:00,280 --> 00:05:00,960
Paling penting.

72
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:01,640
Diletakkan di mana?

73
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:04,240
Dewi bilang,
harus diletakkan di bawah bantal.

74
00:05:04,760 --> 00:05:05,240
Oke.

75
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,560
Bibi, apakah kita masih tetap
mendesak kehamilannya?

76
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:12,400
Nyawa saja tidak terjamin,
untuk apa mendesaknya?

77
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,160
Bibi, awas!

78
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:17,960
Dasar mulutmu ini.

79
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:18,480
Ibu, ada apa?

80
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:20,280
Ibu baik-baik saja, 'kan?

81
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:22,240
Ibu tidak kesakitan, 'kan?

82
00:05:22,320 --> 00:05:22,800
Jangan kemari!

83
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,080
Tidak apa-apa.

84
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:27,520
Aku takut kalian kesakitan.

85
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:28,360
Lantainya dingin.

86
00:05:29,640 --> 00:05:30,720
Kami suka berbaring di lantai.

87
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:32,200
- Benar.
- Jangan kemari.

88
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:33,560
Tidak apa-apa.

89
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,520
Ranjangnya terlalu empuk.

90
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:38,360
Pinggangku jadi sakit.

91
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:40,360
Itu...

92
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:41,480
Itu...

93
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:43,160
Aku pergi dulu.

94
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:44,720
Pergilah.

95
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:01,440
Kau bilang pemasokan ceri tahun ini
tidak memenuhi permintaan

96
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:02,960
dan harga pembelian yang disepakati
tidak rendah?

97
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,560
Baik, aku mengerti.

98
00:06:14,520 --> 00:06:15,440
Apa yang kau katakan tadi?

99
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:17,360
Sayang.

100
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,680
Tadi aku...

101
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,880
Kenapa, Sayang?

102
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:26,280
Chun'er dan ibu melihatku
seperti bertemu hantu.

103
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,200
Bagaimana mungkin?

104
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:31,920
Aku tidak pernah melihat
hantu secantik ini.

105
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,000
Tidak pernah.

106
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:34,960
Jangan terus-terusan menyesatkanku.

107
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:37,000
Bagaimana kalau

108
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:39,280
kau bantu aku memata-matai situasi?

109
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:41,120
Oke.

110
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:42,560
Kalau kau sudah bicara begitu,

111
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:43,560
apakah aku bisa tidak pergi?

112
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:44,680
Aku akan pergi melihatnya.

113
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:45,560
Kau tidur dulu.

114
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:47,600
Jangan tunggu aku.

115
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:56,960
Jiahui.

116
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:59,080
Bagaimana kalau kau dan Jingjing
kembali ke kota dulu?

117
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,280
- Ibu...
- Peramal bilang,

118
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:03,120
kakak ipar adalah bintang tunggal.

119
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:06,840
Jika dia berada di sini, kita bisa mati.

120
00:07:08,840 --> 00:07:09,920
Kau harus percaya.

121
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:12,680
Dewi bilang, aku akan
mengalami bencara hari ini.

122
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:13,640
Kuberi tahu padamu.

123
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:16,320
Tadi bingkai foto itu tiba-tiba jatuh.

124
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,240
Aku berada di bawah bingkai foto itu.

125
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,680
Kalau Chun'er tidak menarikku,

126
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,840
aku tidak bisa mellihatmu lagi hari ini.

127
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:23,880
Bingkai foto?

128
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:36,200
(Empat sekrup terlepas secara bersamaan.)

129
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,080
(Ini adalah perbuatan manusia, 'kan?)


